if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0ab8d3707d9fe112d716ba9ef0eb1a1df03cfb","tid":2289324,"uid":125670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"有 不過愈黎愈少 就快做過1個月"},{"pid":"8ad3f5b44f8d5f2aceb48d997933212b9f69b65e","tid":2289324,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:06:03.000Z","msg":"我同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我幫佢地補鑊多過做自己嘢。<br />\n我有理由懷疑佢地腦退化。<br />\n唔帶腦返工都正常。<br />\n但佢地冇腦到，公司有蒸爐俾佢哋蒸飯，佢哋成日放兜飯入去唔識襟著個蒸爐。轉身做嘢到夠鐘放飯先發現兜飯仲係雪水咁凍。<br />\n跟著成日唔記得自己電話放邊。<br />\n收票，抬頭唔係自己公司名都照收。<br />\n收錢唔記得找錢。<br />\n唔識乘數表。<br />\n唔識搭車（今日仲問我中環碼頭係咪嚮金屎荊廣場果度）<br />\n又唔識分勞工假定銀行假。<br />\n又唔知原來如果公眾假期係星期日就有補假。<br />\n一個50歲一個60歲，老細話俾人情味唔好炒佢哋結果我返工要湊住佢兩隻老嘢。"},{"pid":"d93b6f358df5d96dfe377cb2b76c98b0b5585c5e","tid":2289324,"uid":246787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:08:23.000Z","msg":"今日啱啱返左4 星期 仲係做得好慢 交完冇次唔使個senior改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8bacaade3a6b5ce915725ff0fef676f7c30162","tid":2289324,"uid":212878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d91eee5bde623897ef5720a9c7a347d074526cd","tid":2289324,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"有時公司用開某個方法on9<br />\n我有時諗到好方法解決，最後會比老細話錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"腦細話你蠢你就係蠢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D 細永遠都係蠢 最叻係佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cd1c5cbf7d856d932429b998d48f42f7825f6d","tid":2289324,"uid":128882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad3f5b44f8d5f2aceb48d997933212b9f69b65e","tid":228932